splunk> blaze
A blazingly fast frontend with key bindings using the http://www.tornadoweb.org web framework and http://www.splunk.com search engine.

Put this in your pipe and smoke it!

Installation:
Tornado:
http://www.tornadoweb.org/
Splunk:
http://www.splunk.com/download
Splunk Python SDK:
http://code.google.com/p/splunk-python-sdk/
Run:
python splunkblaze.py
Surf:
http://localhost:8888

Know Issues:
-Safari key bindings not working.
